2026-04-22 18:18:07.856+03:00 DEBUG [http-nio-8080-exec-5] o.s.jdbc.core.JdbcTemplate - Executing prepared SQL statement [SELECT t.ticket_id, m.group_msg_id AS request_number,
       COALESCE(
